com.braintreegateway
Class CreditCardGateway

java.lang.Object
  com.braintreegateway.CreditCardGateway

public class CreditCardGateway
extends java.lang.Object

Provides methods to create, delete, find, and update CreditCard objects. This class does not need to be instantiated directly. Instead, use BraintreeGateway.creditCard() to get an instance of this class: 

 BraintreeGateway gateway = new BraintreeGateway(...);
 gateway.creditCard().create(...)
